{"tid":1290032,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［總結］Tvb邊個都可以屌，就係唔可以屌林泳淘","createTime":"2019-07-06T10:43:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T17:15:17.000Z","uid":43785,"like":1337,"dislike":91,"uniUserReply":108,"replies":[{"pid":"2d8ef3124d1ff5b0ffb36f36aa80e9c794fa4fb2","tid":1290032,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T10:43:46.000Z","msg":"以後Tvb邊個都可以鬧，就係唔可以鬧林泳淘。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全個tvb咁多個人，反送中事件真係得佢一個人算最有良心<br />\n另一個就係周柏豪，佢都係叫人做選民炸。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/amXeunq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FamXeunq.jpg&h=f27cf3cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人哋為咗反送中， 比無線暫停一個月工作 ，冇一個月SHOW錢。畀班建制派投訴到佢冇工開<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SD7aM9y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSD7aM9y.jpg&h=d8c247f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自從選美過後就半紅不黑被編入東張西望做主持。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ck909nP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fck909nP.png&h=c52e3442&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近年稍為有返少少起息， 開始有戲比佢拍 ，但今日真係，唉！ <br />\n仲要畀同路人誤會佢，明明你哋連登仔都冇人損失得勁過佢，佢為咗反送中呢件事冇咗成個月人工，佢都係義士黎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望各位支持一下tvb嘅民主女神林泳淘<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DxVzuny.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDxVzuny.jpg&h=15490811&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5fb3758c50baed48b7b5d3f2e756bc2370eac4c5","tid":1290032,"uid":51041,"like":439,"dislike":24,"score":415,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T10:45:28.000Z","msg":"但我最想屌泳淘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90e615fe4a89c46ad2219bc7058ef4480b25d1f3","tid":1290032,"uid":43785,"like":104,"dislike":9,"score":95,"quote"